

Progress Energy Inc: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















progress energy inc
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Utilities
Industry: Utilities
Sub-Industry: Integrated Utilities
Progress Energy, Inc. is an integrated electric utility that provides energy and energy-related products and services in the Southeast United States.  The Company serves electric and gas customers in the Carolinas and in Florida.




